# Project Structure

Read `PROJECT.md` at the start of every task for current element registry and status.

## Route folders (mandatory files)

Every route under `app/` MUST have:

```
app/(group)/[route]/
  page.tsx        # Server Component — initial data fetch here
  loading.tsx     # REQUIRED — Suspense fallback
  _components/    # Page-only components (not reusable elsewhere)
```

## Component placement

| Situation | Location |
|-----------|----------|
| Reusable now or likely later | `components/` |
| Single page, no future reuse | `app/.../ _components/` |
| shadcn primitives | `components/ui/` |
| Generic error/warning UI | `components/feedback/` |
| Providers (Query, etc.) | `components/providers/` |

**Promotion rule:** Agar `_components/` wala component doosri jagah chahiye → `components/` mein move karo, dono jagah import karo.

## Pages

- `page.tsx` = Server Component (default). `'use client'` sirf jab interaction/state chahiye.
- Initial data fetch `page.tsx` mein via `lib/services/*` — Supabase directly mat call karo page se; service function use karo.
- Client interactivity ke liye alag client component banao (`_components/` ya `components/`).

## After every change

Update `PROJECT.md` element registry + changelog.
